    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaa3",
      "text": "Hatena2013-01-24",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaa4",
      "text": "code:hatena",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaa5",
      "text": " <body>",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaa6",
      "text": " *1359000715*僕のポモドーロアルゴリズム",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaa7",
      "text": " 明確に言語化するのが改善の第一歩ということで、僕がどうやっているかを言語化してみた。",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaa8",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaa9",
      "text": " ちなみに僕の記法では□はタスクの頭に書くチェックボックス、◯は25分を表すポモドーロ。装備としては「iPhoneデフォルトのタイマーで25分カウントダウン」「<a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003COV2X0/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=247&creative=7399&creativeASIN=B003COV2X0&linkCode=as2&tag=nishiohirokaz-22\">ふせん(38mm×50mm）</a>」「<a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000MWW6NA/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=247&creative=7399&creativeASIN=B000MWW6NA&linkCode=as2&tag=nishiohirokaz-22\">消音ヘッドホン</a>」「集中力が増しそうな曲22分+リラックス系4分のプレイリスト」という感じ。",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaaa",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaab",
      "text": " >|c|",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaac",
      "text": " 準備:",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaad",
      "text": " 　順不同に実行{",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaae",
      "text": " 　　□25分のタイマーを開始する",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaaf",
      "text": " 　　□TODOリストから1つ選び、25分で達成できそうなゴールを付箋に書く、このタスクが1ポモドーロと見積もった印に◯を書く",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddab0",
      "text": " 　　□(オプショナル)ヘッドホンを付け、25分のプレイリストを再生する",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddab1",
      "text": " 　}",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddab2",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddab3",
      "text": " // 例外ハンドラ登録",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddab4",
      "text": " 割り込みがあったら goto 割り込み",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddab5",
      "text": " タイマーが鳴ったら goto タイマー",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddab6",
      "text": " 予定していたゴールが達成されたら goto ゴール達成",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddab7",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddab8",
      "text": " タスク実行:",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddab9",
      "text": " 　□集中して作業する",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaba",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddabb",
      "text": " 割り込み:",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddabc",
      "text": " 　if(それはこのポモドーロが終わってから処理してもよいか？){",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddabd",
      "text": " 　　□付箋に書く",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddabe",
      "text": " 　　goto タスク実行  // 作業に戻る",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddabf",
      "text": " 　}else{",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddac0",
      "text": " 　　□割り込みを処理する",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddac1",
      "text": " 　　if(割り込み作業が短くてタスクにすんなり戻れそう？){",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddac2",
      "text": " 　　　goto タスク実行  // 作業に戻る",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddac3",
      "text": " 　　}else{",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddac4",
      "text": " 　　　□ タイムボックスが完成しなかったという意味で◯をバツじるしで消す",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddac5",
      "text": " 　　　□ タイマー止める",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddac6",
      "text": " 　　　goto 準備  // 次のタスク",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddac7",
      "text": " 　　}",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddac8",
      "text": " 　}",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddac9",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaca",
      "text": " ゴール達成:",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddacb",
      "text": " 　おめでとう！タスクを予定より早く完了させたよ！",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddacc",
      "text": " 　□タスクを完了した印に、打ち消し線で消す",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddacd",
      "text": " 　if(残り時間が10分未満){",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddace",
      "text": " 　　□作業の過程で得た知識をメモするとか、フセンを片付けるとか、",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddacf",
      "text": " 　　　作業が済んだ旨のメールを送るとか、git pushするとか、タスクに関連する細かい作業をする。",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddad0",
      "text": " 　}else{",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddad1",
      "text": " 　　□ タイムボックスが完成しなかったという意味で◯をバツじるしで消す",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddad2",
      "text": " 　　□ タイマー止める",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddad3",
      "text": " 　　goto 準備  // 次のタスク",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddad4",
      "text": " 　}",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddad5",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddad6",
      "text": " タイマーが鳴った:",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddad7",
      "text": " 　おめでとう！25分間集中して作業できたよ！",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddad8",
      "text": " 　□25分間集中した印に、◯に斜め線を入れる",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddad9",
      "text": " 　if(タスクもちょうど終わった){",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddada",
      "text": " 　　おめでとう！見積もりもバッチリだ！",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddadb",
      "text": " 　　goto 準備  // 次のタスク",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddadc",
      "text": " 　}else if(切りのいいところまで10分未満で終わると思う){",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddadd",
      "text": " 　　□タイマーを開始する(実際のところどれくらいかかったか計測するため)",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddade",
      "text": " 　　// 例外ハンドラ登録",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddadf",
      "text": " 　　タイマーが鳴ったら goto タイマー2回目",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddae0",
      "text": " 　　□キリのいいところまでやる",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddae1",
      "text": " 　　goto 準備  // 次のタスク",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddae2",
      "text": " 　}else{",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddae3",
      "text": " 　　1ポモドーロやってみたことで知識が得られた。もっとよい見積ができるようになったはず。",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddae4",
      "text": " 　　goto 再見積",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddae5",
      "text": " 　}",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddae6",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddae7",
      "text": " タイマー2回目:",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddae8",
      "text": " 　おめでとう！25分間集中して作業できたよ！",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddae9",
      "text": " 　□25分間集中した印に、◯に斜め線を入れる",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaea",
      "text": " 　残念ながら見積もりの精度はあまりよくないようだ。ドツボにはまってる？",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaeb",
      "text": " 　□お茶を入れに行く、トイレにいく、散歩するなどして仕切りなおし",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaec",
      "text": " 　goto 再見積",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaed",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaee",
      "text": " 再見積:",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaef",
      "text": " 　□残りのタスクに掛かる時間を見積もりなおす。",
      "created": 1358953200,
      "updated": 1358953200,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2faff09e00003ddaf0",
      "text": " 　　そのタスクが予想より時間コストが高いと分かった。",
      "created": 1358953200,
